			<p><a href="http://youtu.be/cDeEvFYHK_k"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-12124" src="http://livhaven.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/slide1_video.jpg" alt="slide1_video" width="297" height="176" /></a>It is passionate and committed people who have made and continue to make Livingston &amp; Haven a leading industrial technology provider. Our associates are problem solvers at heart, always meet the demands of a good challenge, and are impacting lives both inside and outside of the walls of the company.</p>
<p>If you are an industry leader looking to advance your career with an innovative, cutting-edge company, we would like to hear from you. To be considered for employment, please read over the current job openings, complete the Application Forms and submit them along with your current resume; complete with salary history to Human Resources.</p>
<p><a href="/our-culture/">Learn more about our culture »</a></p>

		</div>
	</div>
<h3 style="font-size: 28px;color: #005643;line-height: 36px;text-align: left" class="vc_custom_heading">Current Openings</h3>
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>Job Opening: <a href="/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Outside-Sales-Fluid-Power-Account-Manager-ETN.pdf" target="_blank">Account Manager (Eastern TN)</a></p>
<p>Job Opening: <a href="/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Microsoft-Word-Hydraulics-Design-Engineer.docx.pdf" target="_blank">Hydraulics Design Engineer</a></p>

		</div>
	</div>
<h3 style="font-size: 28px;color: #005643;line-height: 36px;text-align: left" class="vc_custom_heading">Associate Development Program</h3>
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Are you a recent college graduate?  Are you interested in making a difference in the world utilizing engineering as the means to provide innovative solutions?  Do you want to play a role in the successful future of U.S. manufacturing?</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">The Livingston &amp; Haven Associate Development Program (ADP) was created for candidates looking to make a difference, who demonstrate our cultural values, and have a desire to learn about technologies that are continually redefining the world in which we live.  The program has start dates in January and June each year.  Accepted participants go through a 6-month training program where they are given the opportunity to work throughout the organization.  During this time ADP participants are given feedback regarding their progress and have regular conversations about how they see their degrees intersect with real-world experience.  Following the 6-month program, candidates have the opportunity to discuss if a role within Livingston &amp; Haven is the right fit for them.  </span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">To find out more about the program, <a href="/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Associate-Development-Program.pdf" target="_blank">click here</a>.    </span></p>

		</div>
	</div>
<h3 style="font-size: 28px;color: #005643;line-height: 36px;text-align: left" class="vc_custom_heading">Apply Now</h3>
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>Any submitted information will go to our Human Resources Department where we will evaluate your skills and experience. If you are qualified for our open position, we may contact you for more information. Livingston and Haven is an equal opportunity employer and Affirmative Action employer. We do not discriminate in any of our employment decisions. Because we are an Affirmative Action employer we would like to ask you to complete the Voluntary Self ID form along with the Employment Application. If you choose not to give us this information, this decision will not have any bearing on any consideration that we may give you for one of our open positions.</p>
<p><a href="/careers/employment-application/" target="_blank">Apply Online</a></p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Application-Voluntary-Self-Id-Forms.pdf" target="_blank">Download Employment Application</a></p>
<p>In compliance with ADA Amendments Act (ADAAA), if you have a disability and would like to request an accommodation in order to apply for a position with Livingston &amp; Haven, please call 704-588-3670 or email HR@LivHaven.com.</p>
<p>We will consider all qualified applicants regardless of age, race, color, national origin, sex, religion, veteran status, disability, sexual orientation, gender identity or any other legally protected status.</p>
